ead. It bridges gaps between efficient adaptation (adapters), contextual prompting (IC-XLT), and meta-generalization (X-METRA-ADA), but uniquely integrates them into a unified, parameter-invariant solution for multilingual, multi-domain translation—an unmet need in real-world deployment.",
